cs195n
Interface LevelData

public interface LevelData

A generic interface for a level that contains entities and connections. You shouldn't implement this interface or try to construct a LevelData. Instead, use CS195NLevelReader to read a LevelData from a file, then traverse the LevelData you get and convert it to your game's classes. DO NOT MODIFY UNDER ANY CIRCUMSTANCES.

Author:
zdavis
